<font color="yellow">Take a look.</font>

39
00:02:32,019 --> 00:02:33,049
<font color="yellow">(Divorce Registration Form)</font>

40
00:02:34,189 --> 00:02:35,789
<font color="yellow">I've done everything I can...</font>

41
00:02:37,849 --> 00:02:40,659
<font color="yellow">for you two with the result of this retrial.</font>

42
00:02:41,519 --> 00:02:42,519
<font color="yellow">From now on,</font>

43
00:02:43,219 --> 00:02:44,849
