45
00:02:49,219 --> 00:02:50,249
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

46
00:02:50,489 --> 00:02:52,919
<font color="yellow">You'll be away from him only for a short time.</font>

47
00:02:53,789 --> 00:02:55,289
<font color="yellow">After the election,</font>

48
00:02:55,649 --> 00:02:58,389
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure you two can get married again.</font>

49
00:03:00,219 --> 00:03:01,649
<font color="yellow">Where's Il Jae right now?</font>

50
00:03:02,019 --> 00:03:04,819
<font color="yellow">He'll go back to the prison first and leave from there.</font>

51
00:03:06,219 --> 00:03:08,049
<font color="yellow">I'm going over right now. Get ready.</font>

52
00:03:08,049 --> 00:03:09,149
<font color="yellow">Ji Soo.</font>

53
00:03:09,849 --> 00:03:11,019
<font color="yellow">Don't go.</font>

54
00:03:11,019 --> 00:03:13,119
<font color="yellow">We are still lawfully wedded.</font>

55
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:15,519
<font color="yellow">He doesn't have anyone else.</font>

56
00:03:15,519 --> 00:03:17,749
<font color="yellow">If the reporters find you there,</font>

57
00:03:18,289 --> 00:03:19,289
<font color="yellow">I become...</font>

58
00:03:19,689 --> 00:03:21,819
<font color="yellow">a liar from the first day...</font>

59
00:03:23,019 --> 00:03:25,249
<font color="yellow">of my election campaign.</font>

60
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,949
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

61
00:03:33,689 --> 00:03:34,889
<font color="yellow">It's me, Gi Tan.</font>

62
00:03:37,019 --> 00:03:38,289
<font color="yellow">Can we meet right now?</font>

63
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:44,149
<font color="yellow">I saw that you made a very big decision.</font>

64
00:03:46,419 --> 00:03:50,319
<font color="yellow">A Firestone that can't start a fire is nothing but a stone.</font>

65
00:03:51,219 --> 00:03:52,819
<font color="yellow">I'm going on a long journey.</font>

66
00:03:53,589 --> 00:03:55,949
<font color="yellow">I can't carry around stones.</font>

67
00:03:56,049 --> 00:03:57,619
<font color="yellow">That's why I wanted to see you.</font>

68
00:03:58,619 --> 00:03:59,889
<font color="yellow">I want...</font>

69
00:04:00,549 --> 00:04:02,249
<font color="yellow">to light up your journey.</font>

70
00:04:04,619 --> 00:04:08,189
<font color="yellow">Will you become my Firestone in Il Jae's place?</font>

71
00:04:08,189 --> 00:04:10,419
<font color="yellow">I'll light up brighter than he did.</font>

72
00:04:11,189 --> 00:04:13,519
<font color="yellow">You probably need a lot of money for your campaign.</font>

73
00:04:13,619 --> 00:04:16,589
<font color="yellow">Money is even less trustworthy than people.</font>

74
00:04:18,119 --> 00:04:20,019
<font color="yellow">I don't even trust you.</font>

75
00:04:21,119 --> 00:04:24,389
<font color="yellow">How can I accept money from you for my election campaign?</font>

76
00:04:26,019 --> 00:04:27,019
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon.</font>

77
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:31,249
<font color="yellow">I want to talk in private with Mr Hwang.</font>

78
00:04:33,389 --> 00:04:34,459
<font color="yellow">We should leave.</font>

79
00:04:36,219 --> 00:04:38,189
<font color="yellow">Yes, you can leave.</font>

80
00:04:50,189 --> 00:04:51,719
<font color="yellow">I'll be honest with you.</font>

81
00:04:52,219 --> 00:04:53,789
<font color="yellow">As a businessman,</font>

82
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:57,219
<font color="yellow">I only use money where I'm certain of its purpose.</font>

83
00:04:57,619 --> 00:04:59,819
<font color="yellow">Are you saying you'll help me become a president...</font>

84
00:05:00,789 --> 00:05:02,989
<font color="yellow">and take advantage of it when I'm in power?</font>

85
00:05:03,589 --> 00:05:05,349
<font color="yellow">Out of all the conglomerate leaders in the country,</font>

86
00:05:05,689 --> 00:05:08,019
<font color="yellow">there isn't a single person who isn't an ex-convict.</font>

87
00:05:10,219 --> 00:05:12,459
<font color="yellow">Having the president on my side would be the best.</font>

88
00:05:12,549 --> 00:05:13,749
<font color="yellow">All those people...</font>

89
00:05:14,219 --> 00:05:15,959
<font color="yellow">end up getting arrested...</font>

90
00:05:16,589 --> 00:05:18,489
<font color="yellow">for trusting in people like me.</font>

91
00:05:18,489 --> 00:05:20,489
<font color="yellow">However, their companies would have grown by then already.</font>

92
00:05:21,789 --> 00:05:25,189
<font color="yellow">Korean law can be generous in front of money.</font>

93
00:05:25,549 --> 00:05:27,049
<font color="yellow">As a businessman,</font>

94
00:05:27,419 --> 00:05:29,749
<font color="yellow">it's a risk worth taking.</font>

95
00:05:29,749 --> 00:05:31,089
<font color="yellow">You're really...</font>

96
00:05:31,789 --> 00:05:33,419
<font color="yellow">forward.</font>

97
00:05:33,619 --> 00:05:36,519
<font color="yellow">I'm not as forward as you who threw away your son-in-law...</font>

98
00:05:37,449 --> 00:05:39,089
<font color="yellow">to become the president.</font>

99
00:05:56,149 --> 00:05:58,719
<font color="yellow">- I used to be with the NIS as well. - I already know.</font>

100
00:05:59,119 --> 00:06:01,549
<font color="yellow">You were well spoken of as an NIS agent.</font>

101
00:06:02,019 --> 00:06:03,649
<font color="yellow">Why did you go under Congressman Hwang instead?</font>

102
00:06:03,649 --> 00:06:06,319
<font color="yellow">The world is changing. I should see things eye to eye...</font>

103
00:06:06,719 --> 00:06:08,519
<font color="yellow">in order to survive.</font>

104
00:06:09,849 --> 00:06:13,219
<font color="yellow">Do you believe that this position is suitable for you?</font>

105
00:06:15,749 --> 00:06:19,319
<font color="yellow">You'll always live as the third-in-charge.</font>

106
00:06:19,989 --> 00:06:23,149
<font color="yellow">Congressman Hwang will never throw away Il Jae.</font>

107
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,889
<font color="yellow">What is it that you want to say?</font>

108
00:06:26,389 --> 00:06:29,689
<font color="yellow">As you already know, we want to crush Byun Il Jae.</font>

109
00:06:29,789 --> 00:06:30,819
<font color="yellow">Are you asking me...</font>

110
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:33,349
<font color="yellow">to help you?</font>

111
00:06:33,349 --> 00:06:35,249
<font color="yellow">I don't think there's any reason not to.</font>

112
00:06:35,249 --> 00:06:36,749
<font color="yellow">Nor do I have a reason.</font>

113
00:06:37,449 --> 00:06:39,019
<font color="yellow">I don't mind being the third-in-charge.</font>

114
00:06:40,489 --> 00:06:42,849
<font color="yellow">Sure, you may think so for now.</font>

115
00:06:43,389 --> 00:06:46,519
<font color="yellow">However, things will change once Congressman Hwang becomes President.</font>

116
00:06:47,789 --> 00:06:50,289
<font color="yellow">Power isn't something you can divide...</font>

117
00:06:50,289 --> 00:06:52,189
<font color="yellow">like a cake.</font>

118
00:06:56,949 --> 00:07:00,149
<font color="yellow">You'll be eaten up by the second-in-charge.</font>

119
00:07:00,719 --> 00:07:04,789
<font color="yellow">It's even more certain with Byun Il Jae.</font>

120
00:07:12,549 --> 00:07:13,619
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

121
00:07:14,419 --> 00:07:15,849
<font color="yellow">I'll be right down.</font>

122
00:07:20,149 --> 00:07:23,249
<font color="yellow">Make sure you separate Il Jae from Congressman Hwang for good.</font>

123
00:07:23,989 --> 00:07:26,819
<font color="yellow">If we help, it's definitely possible.</font>

124
00:07:28,219 --> 00:07:29,419
<font color="yellow">I'll be waiting for your call.</font>

125
00:07:37,489 --> 00:07:39,189
<font color="yellow">(Korea Penitentiary)</font>

126
00:07:53,689 --> 00:07:56,549
<font color="yellow">I was wondering who would come and greet me.</font>

127
00:07:57,989 --> 00:07:59,819
<font color="yellow">I didn't know it would be you.</font>

128
00:08:01,219 --> 00:08:03,449
<font color="yellow">- Lawyer Min. - Yes.</font>

129
00:08:04,389 --> 00:08:07,649
<font color="yellow">This is tofu made from organic beans.</font>

130
00:08:07,649 --> 00:08:09,149
<font color="yellow">It's super expensive.</font>

131
00:08:09,149 --> 00:08:12,889
<font color="yellow">Anyway, have some of this and never commit crimes again.</font>

132
00:08:18,689 --> 00:08:20,789
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you?</font>

133
00:08:20,789 --> 00:08:23,289
<font color="yellow">You should be more respectful for the people who bought it.</font>

134
00:08:27,289 --> 00:08:28,489
<font color="yellow">Gosh, it smells.</font>

135
00:08:29,389 --> 00:08:31,589
<font color="yellow">It seems like the tofu has gone bad.</font>

136
00:08:31,589 --> 00:08:34,219
<font color="yellow">We probably had it out in the hot weather for too long.</font>

137
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:38,719
<font color="yellow">It's really delicious if you eat it when it's just made.</font>

138
00:08:41,349 --> 00:08:45,089
<font color="yellow">I doubt you came here just to give me some tofu.</font>

139
00:08:45,089 --> 00:08:46,689
<font color="yellow">We came to visit a prisoner.</font>

140
00:08:47,219 --> 00:08:49,119
<font color="yellow">Your secretary, Oh Choong Dong.</font>

141
00:08:52,149 --> 00:08:55,689
<font color="yellow">Are you trying to get something out from Choong Dong?</font>

142
00:08:55,689 --> 00:08:58,119
<font color="yellow">I bet he knows the best about...</font>

143
00:08:58,419 --> 00:09:01,189
<font color="yellow">all the crimes you've committed so far.</font>

144
00:09:02,719 --> 00:09:04,949
<font color="yellow">Don't be so foolish, Lawyer Oh.</font>

145
00:09:04,949 --> 00:09:08,619
<font color="yellow">There is no way he will betray me even if the world comes to an end.</font>

146
00:09:08,619 --> 00:09:10,489
<font color="yellow">The thing with betrayal is,</font>

147
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:13,019
<font color="yellow">it always happens with the person you trust the most.</font>

148
00:09:13,719 --> 00:09:16,219
<font color="yellow">Congressman Hwang gave up on you...</font>

149
00:09:16,219 --> 00:09:17,919
<font color="yellow">and Gun Woo turned his back on you.</font>

150
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:21,059
<font color="yellow">How can you be so sure that Choong Dong won't betray you?</font>

151
00:09:23,289 --> 00:09:25,119
<font color="yellow">I realised it now.</font>

152
00:09:25,119 --> 00:09:29,749
<font color="yellow">A dignified strategy won't work for someone like you.</font>

153
00:09:30,219 --> 00:09:33,689
<font color="yellow">I won't be so careful with my strategies now.</font>

154
00:09:33,819 --> 00:09:35,849
<font color="yellow">Since there was a final ruling,</font>

155
00:09:36,189 --> 00:09:38,219
<font color="yellow">you can't convict me on the same charges.</font>

156
00:09:38,889 --> 00:09:42,189
<font color="yellow">What will you put me in jail for next time?</font>

157
00:09:42,189 --> 00:09:44,849
<font color="yellow">That's not what's important.</font>

158
00:09:44,949 --> 00:09:47,349
<font color="yellow">What's important is, when will you be released...</font>

159
00:09:47,349 --> 00:09:49,149
<font color="yellow">next time, if at all?</font>

160
00:09:50,059 --> 00:09:52,689
<font color="yellow">You won't ever get to taste tofu for your release again.</font>

161
00:09:53,219 --> 00:09:57,519
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure you rot in prison for the rest of your life.</font>

162
00:09:58,449 --> 00:09:59,519
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh.</font>

163
00:10:00,119 --> 00:10:03,789
<font color="yellow">Do you know what the biggest ordeal from the Pandora's box was?</font>

164
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:07,389
<font color="yellow">It's the one that came out last. Hope.</font>

165
00:10:08,119 --> 00:10:09,789
<font color="yellow">Because of hope,</font>

166
00:10:10,649 --> 00:10:12,489
<font color="yellow">a whole new struggle begins.</font>

167
00:10:14,289 --> 00:10:17,449
<font color="yellow">You should rid yourself of any useless hopes.</font>

168
00:10:17,689 --> 00:10:18,919
<font color="yellow">You better...</font>

169
00:10:20,289 --> 00:10:21,849
<font color="yellow">mark those words.</font>

170
00:10:23,149 --> 00:10:27,319
<font color="yellow">Because the days when you struggle from hope...</font>

171
00:10:27,589 --> 00:10:29,059
<font color="yellow">will be upon you soon.</font>

172
00:10:30,889 --> 00:10:34,519
<font color="yellow">The taxis don't come around here much.</font>

173
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:37,319
<font color="yellow">You have to go down that hill for the bus station.</font>

174
00:10:38,189 --> 00:10:39,789
<font color="yellow">You know how much buses cost, right?</font>

175
00:10:39,789 --> 00:10:41,749
<font color="yellow">We'll be late for our visit. Let's go.</font>

176
00:10:41,749 --> 00:10:43,349
<font color="yellow">Okay, we should go.</font>

177
00:10:43,349 --> 00:10:48,519
<font color="yellow">Gosh. You don't have a single person to pick you up. How sad.</font>

178
00:11:19,749 --> 00:11:22,219
<font color="yellow">I'll decline this visit. Please cancel it.</font>

179
00:11:22,589 --> 00:11:25,489
<font color="yellow">Officer Kim, how is your baby?</font>

180
00:11:26,219 --> 00:11:29,449
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, but could you let him stay here...</font>

181
00:11:29,449 --> 00:11:30,849
<font color="yellow">for the visitation hour?</font>

182
00:11:30,849 --> 00:11:33,289
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir. Hey, 2757.</font>

183
00:11:44,949 --> 00:11:48,819
<font color="yellow">I won't be opening my mouth until the time's up.</font>

184
00:11:49,589 --> 00:11:51,519
<font color="yellow">Then I'll just ask questions.</font>

185
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:55,689
<font color="yellow">Did you kill my brother?</font>

186
00:11:59,149 --> 00:12:01,489
<font color="yellow">Or did Il Jae murder him...</font>

187
00:12:01,689 --> 00:12:03,319
<font color="yellow">with his own hands?</font>

188
00:12:05,189 --> 00:12:07,889
<font color="yellow">How many did you kill aside from Dong Soo?</font>

189
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,149
<font color="yellow">Two? Three?</font>

190
00:12:10,149 --> 00:12:11,989
<font color="yellow">What on earth are you talking about?</font>

191
00:12:12,489 --> 00:12:15,749
<font color="yellow">I thought you weren't going to talk. Why are you yelling?</font>

192
00:12:16,319 --> 00:12:18,989
<font color="yellow">You killed Gi Tan's parents, too. Am I right?</font>

193
00:12:19,849 --> 00:12:21,789
<font color="yellow">Did you kill Su Do Hospital's Dr Jung Man Ok, too?</font>

194
00:12:21,789 --> 00:12:23,189
<font color="yellow">It wasn't me!</font>

195
00:12:25,089 --> 00:12:27,149
<font color="yellow">Then I guess it was Il Jae.</font>

196
00:12:31,619 --> 00:12:34,449
<font color="yellow">Yap all you want.</font>

197
00:12:35,489 --> 00:12:36,519
<font color="yellow">Officer Kim.</font>

198
00:12:36,889 --> 00:12:38,949
<font color="yellow">You're recording this, right?</font>

199
00:12:39,319 --> 00:12:42,219
<font color="yellow">Make sure you write down "Yap all you want."</font>

200
00:12:42,489 --> 00:12:43,689
<font color="yellow">Yes, Lawyer Min.</font>

201
00:12:44,189 --> 00:12:45,219
<font color="yellow">Oh Choong Dong.</font>

202
00:12:46,049 --> 00:12:48,519
<font color="yellow">When we reveal the truth,</font>

203
00:12:48,519 --> 00:12:53,149
<font color="yellow">Il Jae will blame you for everything.</font>

204
00:12:53,149 --> 00:12:57,619
<font color="yellow">Just to remind you, our country still has the death penalty.</font>

205
00:12:58,819 --> 00:13:01,949
<font color="yellow">While you keep your mouth shut for loyalty,</font>

206
00:13:02,619 --> 00:13:03,819
